[02:17:23] <TheLat> Is it possible to do OpenGL coding for the Switch with glBegin(GL_QUADS); and the like?
[02:18:08] <TheLat> Code samples and the errors I'm getting at compile time are indicating that it is not, but I just want to check
[02:18:33] *** Joins: eggster (~eggster@irchighway.eggy.cc)
[02:43:16] <endrift> I don't think GL_QUADS exists in anything other than 1.x
[02:43:23] *** Joins: mukunda_ (~mukunda@adsl-074-188-202-180.sip.asm.bellsouth.net)
[02:44:29] <endrift> it's not in GLES 1.1, and I'm pretty sure it's not in 2.0 or GL 3.0
[02:45:29] <endrift> ah it's in GL 2.x and below, and that's it
[02:45:38] <endrift> anyway don't use it
